## Development Environment

This project uses [Nix flakes](https://nixos.wiki/wiki/Flakes) for reproducible development environments and [direnv](https://direnv.net/) for automatic environment activation.

### Prerequisites

- [Nix](https://nixos.org/download.html) with flakes enabled
- [direnv](https://direnv.net/)

### Getting Started

1. Allow direnv for this directory:
   ```bash
   direnv allow
   ```

2. Start the development server:
   ```bash
   uvicorn app.main:app --reload
   ```

3. Open your browser to http://localhost:8000
   - API docs: http://localhost:8000/docs
   - Alternative docs: http://localhost:8000/redoc

## Available Commands

- `uvicorn app.main:app --reload` - Start development server with hot reload
- `pytest` - Run tests
- `black .` - Format code with Black
- `flake8 .` - Lint code
- `mypy .` - Type check with mypy

